article.headline: Sam Houston St. 113, Wiley 72
article.story: HUNTSVILLE, Texas (AP) -- Chris Jordan scored 14 points to lead seven scorers in double digits as Sam Houston State beat Wiley College 113-72 on Thursday night. Ryan Griffin added 13 points, Wilder Auguste had 12 and Othello Alford and Ryan Bright scored 11 apiece. Joe Thompson and Eddy Fobbs scored 10 each and Thompson had six assists for Sam Houston State (3-5). Sam Houston State scored 37 points off of 28 Wiley College turnovers. Sylvester Simple scored 20 points and Willie Holloway added 15 for Wiley College (1-4).
